---
title: Sour Cream and Onion Tofu with Roasted Veggies and Creamy Pan Sauce
description: Giving tonight's dinner the favourite sour cream and onion chips treatment. All the tangy onion yumminess without any of the deep frying, this meal comes together in a flavourful flash!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tofu-a-la-creme-sure-et-a-loignon-99911279.jpg
